TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {41377=© 2011 Denville Public Library. All rights reserved., 30055=Are you a Harry Potter fan? Great, because we are, too! We're hosting a Harry Potter Party on Monday, July 15th at 3:00 pm. Test your skills at Harry Potter trivia (for fun prizes!), play some games, and make a cool wizardy craft. This party is open to all ages, but it is best suited toward fans of the books / movies and older children. We want to make sure that we have enough supplies for everyone, so please register below. Expecto Patronum! :-)}
